- Cepat!

217
00:22:05,790 --> 00:22:07,320
- Saya datang!
- "Saya datang!"

218
00:22:07,390 --> 00:22:09,160
Biar betul! Awak nak matikah?

219
00:22:22,270 --> 00:22:23,600
Awak panggil ini makanan ringkas?

220
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:26,840
Patutkah saya pesan salmon lebih awal,
Tuan Ga-on?

221
00:22:26,910 --> 00:22:28,110
